OL,3,CPolice investigate reports of sex acts
OL,4,Con horse over two-year period
OL,6,FPolice have launched an investigation
OL,7,Finto reports of a man committing sex
OL,8,Facts on a horse.
OL,10,FSouth Yorkshire Police say several
OL,11,Fincidents were reported in the Abdy
OL,12,Farea of Rotherham over a two-year
OL,13,Fperiod between January 2024 and
OL,14,FJanuary 2026.
OL,16,FOfficers have released a CCTV image of
OL,17,Fa man they want to find.
OL,19,FHe is described as slim, with short,
OL,20,Fdark hair.
